# CODEOWNERS — OneSell Scout
#
# Determines who is automatically requested for review when a PR touches
# specific paths. Maps to the role responsibilities defined in
# docs/PROJECT-MANAGEMENT.md and .github/copilot-instructions.md.
#
# Format: <pattern>  <@github-username or @org/team>
# The LAST matching pattern wins (GitHub evaluation order).
#
# The human owner @chenning007 is the final reviewer for all paths until
# the team expands. Replace role-specific handles with team members as they join.
# e.g.  @org/architects  or individual GitHub usernames

# ─── Default: human owner reviews everything ──────────────────────────────
*                          @chenning007

# ─── Product / PRD — PM owns ──────────────────────────────────────────────
docs/PRD-*.md              @chenning007
docs/PROJECT-MANAGEMENT.md @chenning007

# ─── Architecture — Architect owns ───────────────────────────────────────
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md       @chenning007
docs/architecture/         @chenning007
docs/guides/               @chenning007

# ─── Copilot & workflow config — human owner reviews all changes ──────────
.github/copilot-instructions.md   @chenning007
.github/instructions/             @chenning007
.github/workflows/                @chenning007
.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/           @chenning007

# ─── Client extraction layer — security-critical ──────────────────────────
onesell-client/src/main/extraction/ExtractionManager.ts   @chenning007
onesell-client/src/main/extraction/ExtractionScriptRegistry.ts  @chenning007
onesell-client/src/main/ipc/                              @chenning007
onesell-client/src/shared/                                @chenning007

# ─── Backend agent pipeline — LLM/tool changes ────────────────────────────
